title: Tootie Against Humanity: Tootie's April 2017 Mix
description:
April saw the debut of "Tootie Against Humanity". Now listen to the mix of the same name. This mix features the theme for the accompanying party event and the music for when a certain card was played (which never was). The highlight of the mix is the good number of 80s songs, as well as a Tootie-created suite of music from a certain video game.

All tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.

Details:
Format: FLAC, level 7
Length: 1:30:32.540
Average bitrate: 787 kbps
Embedded CUE Sheet

Playback verified with foobar2000. Track notes embedded via comment fields and can be accessed with foobar2000. Track CTRB content ratings also included.

Stream Tootie mixes at:
mixcloud.com/CyberTootie/
